<i>adjective</i>: 이쁘다 [이ː쁘다], 예쁘다 [예ː쁘다], 사랑스럽다 [사랑스럽따], 깜찍스럽다 [깜찍쓰럽따], 귀엽다 [귀ː엽따], 귀염성스럽다 [귀ː염썽스럽따] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>이쁘다 [이ː쁘다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pretty; beautiful; comely</dd><br>
<dd>생긴 모양이 눈으로 보기에 좋을 만큼 아름답다.</dd><br>
<dd>The appearance of someone or something looking good and beautiful.</dd><br>
<dd>2. adorable</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 동작, 말투 등이 보기에 사랑스럽고 귀엽다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's behavior, movements, way of speaking, etc., being lovely and cute.</dd><br>
<dd>3. nice; good</dd><br>
<dd>아이가 행동이 바르고 말을 잘 들어서 흐뭇하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A child making one feel satisfied because he/she behaves correctly and does what he/she is told.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>예쁘다 [예ː쁘다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. pretty; beautiful; comely</dd><br>
<dd>생긴 모양이 눈으로 보기에 좋을 만큼 아름답다.</dd><br>
<dd>The appearance of someone or something looking good and beautiful.</dd><br>
<dd>2. adorable</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 동작, 말투 등이 보기에 사랑스럽고 귀엽다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's behavior, movements, way of speaking, etc., being lovely and cute.</dd><br>
<dd>3. nice; good</dd><br>
<dd>아이가 행동이 바르고 말을 잘 들어서 흐뭇하다.</dd><br>
<dd>A child making one feel satisfied because he/she behaves correctly and does what he/she is told.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사랑스럽다 [사랑스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>lovely; adorable</dd><br>
<dd>사랑을 느낄 만큼 귀엽다.</dd><br>
<dd>So cute as to evoke a feeling of affection.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>깜찍스럽다 [깜찍쓰럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cute; adorable</dd><br>
<dd>생김새나 모습이 작고 귀엽다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's look or appearance being small and cute.</dd><br>
<dd>2. precocious</dd><br>
<dd>행동이나 태도가 나이나 몸집에 비해 약삭빠르고 영악하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's behavior or attitude being quick-witted and shrewd for one's age and build.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>귀엽다 [귀ː엽따]</dt><br>
<dd>cute; adorable; sweet</dd><br>
<dd>보기에 예쁘거나 사랑스럽다.</dd><br>
<dd>Pretty and adorable.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>귀염성스럽다 [귀ː염썽스럽따]</dt><br>
<dd>lovable; adorable</dd><br>
<dd>보기에 예쁘고 사랑스러운 데가 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Looking pretty and lovely.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>